Overview of changes for mdbus 2.3.2
===============================================================================
* After a long period of inactivity, this project is alive again. We start
with a better manpage and then see what comes along.

Overview of changes for mdbus 2.1.0
===============================================================================

* ported to use gdbus instead of dbus-glib (no dependency on dbus-glib is needed anymore)
* due to the port to gdbus parameters for methods needs to be written in GVariant syntax
  (see glib documentation for more information)
